. You get 3 percent cash back on purchases made at the Apple Store, and 2 percent back on all other purchases made using Apple Pay. If you use the physical Apple Card, you’ll only get 1 percent back.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n</div>","author":"Roman Loyola","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"6f568fc3f4d0c89fd4ceb5520b32e16a455384e7809bb70f9d31480dc9897912","category":"Apple"}